# I18n

Read [docs/I18N.md](../../docs/I18N.md).

- New translation files use `config/locales/<locale>/<feature>.yml`.
- Do not create new `feature.fr.yml` or `feature.en.yml` files.
- The YAML root must match the locale folder.
- Keep user-facing copy translated through locale keys when touching related code.
- Keep technical documentation and developer-facing text in English.
